---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Powershell = ❤️ - o9">
  <Header />

  <main class="flex flex-col min-h-screen pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <article class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Powershell = ❤️
        </h1>

        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">August 1, 2025</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300"
          >
            PowerShell
          </span>
        </div>

        <p>
          My Powershell Script is now available on GitHub. The Supercharge script is a collection of
          useful PowerShell functions that I've developed over the years to make my development work
          easier and more efficient.
        </p>

        <p>
          You can find it on my GitHub repository: <a
            href="https://github.com/o9-9/supercharge"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Supercharge</a
          >.
        </p>

        <h2>What does it do?</h2>

        <p>The Supercharge script provides a number of useful features:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Enhanced file system navigation</li>
          <li>Productivity shortcuts for common tasks</li>
          <li>Development environment setup and configuration</li>
          <li>Custom prompts and themes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to install</h2>

        <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/o9-9/supercharge.git
cd supercharge
./install.ps1</code></pre>

        <p>Check out the README for more detailed installation instructions and usage examples.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold">Stay updated!</p>
          <p>
            Follow the <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
              >RSS feed</a
            > to get notified about new posts and updates.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
